<br>
I was under the impression that our pets could not proc against Emperor or any boss mob, and not having bane weapons, could not do regular melee damage on emp in particular.  In light of the recent patches does this still hold true? (If there is a post on this already, my search did not turn it up, but I thought I saw something somewhere)<br>
<br>
Emperor in particular...<br>
Presuming the pets are not responsible for any procs or damage, what could be the reasons for summoning up mage (or cleric etc) pets for this encounter...  My brainstorming and suggestions have so far come up with ...<br>
<br>
-They are able to do damage..?<br>
-They just look cool but serve no real purpose.<br>
-Used to keep emp in position (hard to believe)<br>
-Used as a wall to control knockback?<br>
-other?<br>
<br>
My attempts on emp, and opportunity to experiment on him are limited, so finding it out for myself may or may not be possible.  If you dont wish to post any top secret uber strat thats just fine, please post nothing at all.  Speculation as well as fact are welcome.<br>
<br>
